WEBVTT

00:00.139 --> 00:02.724
Previouly, on "Better Call Saul."

00:02.810 --> 00:05.310
I get my money, or neither
of us walk out of here.

00:05.395 --> 00:09.119
I say the word, my nephews pay
a visit to your granddaughter.

00:10.067 --> 00:12.877
I don't ever want to hear the
word "permit" again! Capiche?

00:12.903 --> 00:13.903
It's your funeral, dude!

00:13.987 --> 00:15.114
You're fired!

00:15.139 --> 00:16.238
I'll just pack up...

00:16.323 --> 00:18.217
Partners, you and me!

00:18.242 --> 00:19.101
What about clients?

00:19.126 --> 00:20.269
Mesa Verde.

00:20.294 --> 00:21.827
It'd be a hard sell to
take them with me.

00:21.912 --> 00:24.389
Separate firms under one roof.

00:24.414 --> 00:27.621
You... do things your way,
and I do them mine.

